      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and roughly chop into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Crush <strong>half</strong> your <strong>garlic</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) open by squashing with the side of a knife and remove the skin</p>",
