    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut a piece of <strong>tin foil</strong> approx. the size of an A3 sheet of paper (or two!) and lay out</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped pepper</strong> to the middle with the <strong>crushed</strong> <strong>garlic</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Scrunch the edges of the foil around the pepper to form a sealed parcel[s] and add to one side of a baking tray</p>",
